  "body": "# üêû Bug Report\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nIt isn't possible to enable JSON-HTTP API access from outside since it's always listening on 127.0.0.1 and it isn't possible to change it, is this expected?\r\n\r\n### Has this worked before in a previous version?\r\n\r\nThis change was made on https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/pull/5614\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/d1a1043ef10ffc055b5f9f018cc6633001dba2a6/beacon-chain/node/node.go#L602\r\n\r\nPreviously:\r\n``` \r\ngatewayAddress := fmt.Sprintf(\"0.0.0.0:%d\", gatewayPort) \r\n```\r\n\r\n## üî• Error\r\n\r\n<pre><code>\r\ntime=\"2020-06-10 07:02:16\" level=info msg=\"Logs will be made persistent\" logFileName=\"/data/beacon-chain.log\"\r\ntime=\"2020-06-10 07:02:16\" level=info msg=\"File logging initialized\"\r\ntime=\"2020-06-10 07:02:16\" level=info msg=\"Checking DB\" database-path=\"/data/beaconchaindata\" prefix=node\r\ntime=\"2020-06-10 07:02:16\" level=info msg=\"Starting beacon node\" prefix=node version=\"Prysm/Git commit: 1f20cbb3f0d28d8fea81dc6a968a08d151cb9ece. Built at: 2020-06-10 01:55:33+00:00\"\r\ntime=\"2020-06-10 07:02:16\" level=info msg=\"Starting JSON-HTTP API\" address=\"127.0.0.1:3000\" prefix=gateway\r\ntime=\"2020-06-10 07:02:16\" level=info msg=\"Waiting to reach the validator deposit threshold to start the beacon chain...\" prefix=blockchain\r\ntime=\"2020-06-10 07:02:16\" level=info msg=\"RPC-API listening on port\" address=\"0.0.0.0:4000\" prefix=rpc\r\ntime=\"2020-06-10 07:02:16\" level=warning msg=\"You are using an insecure gRPC connection! Provide a certificate and key to connect securely\" prefix=rpc\r\ntime=\"2020-06-10 07:02:16\" level=info msg=\"Connected to eth1 proof-of-work chain\" endpoint=\"http://goerli-geth.dappnode:8545\" prefix=powchain\r\ntime=\"2020-06-10 07:02:18\" level=info msg=\"Processing deposits from Ethereum 1 chain\" deposits=1024 genesisValidators=1000 prefix=powchain\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n",
